//
//
// Same trap detection engine now runs on ALL three sessions:
//    • Asia ORB    → overnight trap detection
//    • London ORB  → pre-market trap detection
//    • NY ORB      → main session trap detection
//  Same methodology. Three chances per day. One indicator.
//
//  GB PARALLAX v1.0 — Decision HUD
//  "See the real move. Not the fake one."
//  Real losses. Real lessons. Real edge.
//  Built on the battlefield, not in a classroom.
//
//  Designed by GB — Years of live market R&D.
//
//  PARALLAX is NOT an auto-entry system. It is a fighter pilot heads-up display.
//  It detects TRAPS at ORH/ORL breaks by reading candle body direction.
//  It shows you what happened, warns you of traps, and tells you when it's safe.
//  YOU make the final call. PARALLAX removes the stress, not the control.
//
//  CORE METHOD (GB's live-tested edge):
//    1. Price breaks ORH or ORL → BREAK DETECTED (do NOT enter)
//    2. Read next candle body → bearish confirms short, bullish = TRAP
//    3. Count 2-3 confirming candles with matching bodies
//    4. If trap → watch for price to flip to other side → TRAP REVERSAL
//    5. RSI must be in 20-80 safe zone
//    6. SL = swing low/high of last 5-6 candles (NOT ORH/ORL)
//    7. Minimum 50 point target, manage on 1m
// ═════════════════════════════════════════════════
//─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// §1  INPUTS — SESSIONS
//─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

